|                                                           |
|  format_version "1"                                       |
|                                                           |
|  new_manifest [dbd022dc423fd7f473e0fa79842cd9901cc2dd69] <-- manifest id
|                                                           |
|  old_revision: []                                         |
|                                                           |
|  ...                                                      |
|                                                           |
