|                                    \/                     |
|  old_revision [f45add3bfb21cb459d99b6a9c0111df75f6d9f85]  |
|                                                           |
|  ...                                                      |
|                                                           |
+-----------------------------------------------------------+

\____________________________________  _____________________/
