                                    SHA1
                                     ||
+------------------------------------||---------------------+
|                                    ||                     |
|  format_version "1"                ||                     |
|                                    ||                     |
|  new_manifest [2027b4ab2febf98bd9a0||c000a69a8227cdaaf7] <-- manifest id
|                                    \/                     |
|  old_revision [1c83997e7ab40c0df47554c81b7d4e7ee691eb0d]  |
