Prints the heads of branch @var{branch}.

@item Sample output:

@verbatim
28ce076c69eadb9b1ca7bdf9d40ce95fe2f29b61
75156724e0e2e3245838f356ec373c50fa469f1f
@end verbatim

@item Output format:

Zero or more lines, each giving the ID of one head of the given branch.
